<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٢٣١٠ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3997">عَبْدُ اللهِ بْنُ يُوسُفَ: </a>أَخْبَرَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5361">مَالِكٌ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2521">أَبِي حَازِمٍ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2676">سَهْلِ بْنِ سَعْدٍ </a>قَالَ: <span class="c2">«جَاءَتِ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></span></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>⦗١٠١⦘<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">امْرَأَةٌ إِلَى رَسُولِ اللهِ <span class="special">ﷺ</span> فَقَالَتْ:</span> يَا رَسُولَ اللهِ، إِنِّي قَدْ وَهَبْتُ لَكَ مِنْ نَفْسِي.<span class="c5"> فَقَالَ رَجُلٌ:</span> زَوِّجْنِيهَا،<span class="c5"> قَالَ:</span> قَدْ زَوَّجْنَاكَهَا بِمَا مَعَكَ مِنَ الْقُرْآنِ.»<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>